This is an artificial assistance that will help users to assemble a desktop computer. In order to have a better experience with this program, please read the notes below.


There are a few things need to know before beginning:

1.If there is nothing returned, that means there is a typo in your input, please check you input again

2.Please remember to type in "finish shopping" when you stop shopping; otherwise, there might be errors

3.When you want to move to next section, you can just type in section's name

4.If you do not know the commands you can use, you can just type in "instructions"

5.There is no extra modules you need to download

6.Try to follow the instructions provided
